{"tid":722010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[6月29]建造業對人才需求大，輕人要好好裝備自己，把握機遇","createTime":"2018-06-29T06:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T09:51:19.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ac5c10107d2ac01a2c158e266cae7d2ace17c7df","tid":722010,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T06:39:20.000Z","msg":"建造業對人才需求大，業界<span style=\"color: red;\">年輕人要好好裝備自己，把握機遇</span>，參加技能比賽是其中一個好方法。香港建造業議會（下稱「議會」）日前舉辦「香港建造業青年技能大賽」，設砌磚、細木等6個比賽項目，由行內「老行尊」擔任評審。參賽者都凝神屏氣，在各個項目一較高下，當中最年輕的參賽者只有16歲，更勇奪項目冠軍，令人驚喜！<br />\n<br />\n議會執行總監鄭定寕指，<span style=\"color: red;\">不少年輕人有感建造業發展前景良好，有意加入</span>，未來議會將提供更多培訓課程，及舉辦更多活動提升他們的專業技能。有經驗的師傅則可傳授工藝予年輕人，驅使建造業逐步邁向專業化和科技化，為建造業增添新血。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180629/photo/bkn-20180629083043780-0629_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180629083334\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180629083043780-0629_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180629083334&h=6471a74a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180629/bkn-20180629083043780-0629_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180629%2Fbkn-20180629083043780-0629_00822_001.html&d=lsEX9PPb4EQpsGRAxbWurhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=2147d969\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180629/bkn-20180629083043780-0629_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"540842b0c72ccd57c3b96a9e239e5e4933b68a71","tid":722010,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T06:39:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180629/photo/bkn-20180629083043780-0629_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180629083334\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180629083043780-0629_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180629083334&h=6471a74a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b